://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMo7Worb.jpg&h=d73d385d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<ins>10/6 2334 MME指出並沒有收到Deliverllow直接嘅道歉，及其後<span style=\"color: red;\">指出YellowPanda負責人Calvin恐嚇MME外送員的行為</span></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZEqgMg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZEqgMg.jpg&h=884b6bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/mamaeat/473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmamaeat%2F473&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=3662159b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mamaeat/473</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1Tnjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1Tnjf8.jpg&h=adcd4b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/mamaeat/477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmamaeat%2F477&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=6691a314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mamaeat/477</a> <br />\n詳細版可看：<a href=\"https://t.me/mamaeat/475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmamaeat%2F475&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a350fb73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mamaeat/475</a> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>11/6 0138<span style=\"color: red;\"> Calvin於其外送group內作出對此事之回應</span></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2d23rH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2d23rH.jpg&h=8a190e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkuber/8300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkuber%2F8300&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=9dcf7852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkuber/8300</a> <br />\n*因其group已為private group恕未能附上原source，只能附上於Uber救護車的截圖<br />\n<br />\n<ins>11/6 0141 Calvin指出於group內之張貼者<span style=\"color: red;\">「post完即改ac」的行為鬼祟，質疑事件的可信性</span>，但其後